text: Nawab Sir Liaqat Hyat Khan, KCIE (1887-1948) was a British Indian administrator and a Prime Minister of Patiala state in Punjab. He was the son of Nawab Muhammad Hyat Khan and elder brother of Sir Sikandar Hyat Khan. Category:1887 births Category:1948 deaths Category:Indian politicians Category:Punjabi people
title: Liaqat Hayat
